OL,3,C'I do miss it': Prince of Wales
OL,4,Crevisits airbase where he made 'fond
OL,5,Cmemories'
OL,7,FThe Prince of Wales has spoken of
OL,8,F"fond memories" at his former air base
OL,9,Fas he returned to mark its 85th
OL,10,Fanniversary.
OL,12,FWilliam, who wore RAF military pattern
OL,13,Fcamouflage uniform, told trainees at
OL,14,FRAF Valley in Anglesey, North Wales,
OL,15,Fthat he "loved" his time there.
OL,17,FHe was an RAF search and rescue pilot
OL,18,Fat the Holyhead base from 2010 to
OL,19,F2013, when he and the Princess of
OL,20,FWales lived together in Anglesey as
OL,21,Fnewlyweds.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@OO]wD@IOUwD@OO]
