OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1777471868
OL,3,C'I do miss it': Prince of Wales
OL,4,Crevisits airbase where he made 'fond
OL,5,Cmemories'
OL,7,FDuring the visit, he met former
OL,8,Fcolleagues including pilot instructor
OL,9,FBrian Wills and chief maritime
OL,10,Finstructor Andy Batchelor, who said
OL,11,Fthe Prince had expressed his desire to
OL,12,Fget back in the cockpit.
OL,14,FMr Wills said: "In a heartbeat, he
OL,15,Fsaid he'd come back and do it again."
OL,17,FMr Batchelor, who worked with William
OL,18,Fon search and rescue crews, said:
OL,19,F"He's a great guy, friendly, easy to
OL,20,Fget on with, a very competent pilot.
OL,26,@vD@POUwD@eO]{D@AOU
