PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1777471868
OL,3,C'I do miss it': Prince of Wales
OL,4,Crevisits airbase where he made 'fond
OL,5,Cmemories'
OL,7,F"He was very easy to work with. He
OL,8,Fjust wanted to be Will, he was just
OL,9,Fone of the team."
OL,11,FSpeaking to trainees at the station,
OL,12,Fwhich opened in February 1941, William
OL,13,Fsaid: "I loved my time up here. It was
OL,14,Fgreat fun.
OL,16,F"Your time up here will go quickly,
OL,17,Fthat's the thing. You'll look back
OL,18,Fwith fond memories."
OL,20,FHe added: "I do miss it. I miss the
OL,21,Fjob, I miss the camaraderie."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@GOUxD@AOUzD@TO]|D@KOU}D@]O]
