OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1777471868
OL,3,C'I do miss it': Prince of Wales
OL,4,Crevisits airbase where he made 'fond
OL,5,Cmemories'
OL,7,FWilliam, who is Royal Honorary Air
OL,8,FCommodore, watched a parade to mark
OL,9,Fthe 85th anniversary of the RAF
OL,10,Fstation.
OL,12,FHe also met women from the base and
OL,13,Ftold them he was trying to take
OL,14,F"barometer readings" of the
OL,15,Fexperiences of females in the military.
OL,17,FHe said: "Some things have come to my
OL,18,Fattention that I'm not particularly
OL,19,Fhappy about.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@TO]yD@JOU
