CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1777471868
OL,3,C'I do miss it': Prince of Wales
OL,4,Crevisits airbase where he made 'fond
OL,5,Cmemories'
OL,7,F"Are we adopting and evolving the
OL,8,Farmed forces in a way that is suiting
OL,9,Fwomen joining the forces and is it a
OL,10,Fnice place to join?"
OL,12,FThe officers spoke to William about
OL,13,Ftheir experiences, including returning
OL,14,Fto work in the RAF after having
OL,15,Fchildren.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@TO]
